well actually no, i was just about to pose a question here and you got this in before me.<P>What if we had the shapeshift, ut it was illusions, it merely effected cosmetics,and allowed us to be neutral to all as far as aggro was concerned. Any combat woudl drop it of course, but we could get various animals, and possibly enemy races. hate to sound like an EQ chanter, but it would fit with the mind bending idea of the class, or Matter OR body if it is a true shapehift.<P>Even if OTHER casters wears the mighty robes of "Shoot Here" in pvP, at elast WE could look like we were wearing plate for a short time, or maybe just look like a wolf.<P>This does lead me to another thing i am considering suggesting, and wonder what others here think.<P>Dematerialize-<P>Buff in the body line. Instant cast, once every 15 minutes. Earned at every 10 levels, and the duration increases each time..<P>10- 5 seconds, 20- 10 seconds, 30- 15 seconds, 40- 20 seconds, 50- 25 seconds.<P>What it is is an instant cast ability that dematerialises the sorceror. for that time no damage can come to him, but he also can not effect the world around him. he woudl move at a slowed encumbered pace, and all his buffs would drop.<P>Think the Vision from the justice league or Kitty pryde from the X-Men.<P>Think it would help our survival without overpowering us in solo too much?<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
