Illusion spells -- love the idea  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>Dematerialize -- love the idea  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"> One question though -- would we be invisible, or just transparent?  If invisible, I agree that movement rate should be as slow as a stealthed player (although not as slow as encumbered).  If we'll still be visible (just tranparent), I think the movement rate should be normal.  That at least gives us a chance to sprint to safety -- otherwise (if encumbered and partially visible) if we're out in the open we'd be dead anyway (just delaying the inevitable) b/c it'd be hard to run to safety at an encumbred rate.<P>Mirror Image -- love the idea  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"> But it does suffer from the lag problem that was mentioned.<P>--------------------<P>--Kestrel Trebor, Sorceror<BR>The Sacred Brotherhood<BR>"Honor, loyalty, and above all, brotherhood!"<BR>Albion, Percival Server
